### 2. Production-Ready UI (app/page.tsx)
✅ Clean, minimal, professional design (Notion/Linear inspired)
✅ 2-column layout: 260px sidebar + flexible workspace
✅ All functional buttons (no static UI)
✅ 5 theme system: Light, Dark, Forest, Paper, Neo
✅ Dark mode toggle
✅ Subtle animations (150-250ms transitions)
✅ localStorage persistence for projects and preferences
✅ Responsive design
✅ Sequential workflow: Upload → Summary → Tasks → Timeline → Dashboard
✅ Chat Copilot with floating button and drawer
✅ Agent integration using aiAgent.ts (callAIAgent, uploadFiles)
✅ Fallback demo data for graceful error handling

### 3. Integration
✅ Uses existing lib/aiAgent.ts for all AI/chat operations
✅ Proper JSON parsing with code block extraction
✅ State management with React hooks and localStorage
✅ No toast/sonner libraries
✅ No sign-in/OAuth flows
✅ react-icons/fi for all icons

